description:
The epic choice: Edward or Jacob. Now you can show what team you're on with this Team Edward countdown app that shows you how long until the German premiere of The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn Part Two. You can share how long the wait is with your friends. Send directly to TXT, e-mail, or copy to the clipboard. Want to help prove that Edward is a better choice? Download the app and leave a good review. The team app with the highest number downloads & stars wins bragging rights. 

-=-=- 

#3 Fan has no association with the Twilight franchise. 

Support e-mails can be sent to naHQun@gmail.com
